text: Cochliopalpus fimbriatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1928.BioLib.cz - Cochliopalpus fimbriatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1928
